  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I was going to-- in a tuxedo, I didn't give a damn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just-- the guy said, just take off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Took my car, went to the hotel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next morning, the brother comes over, [INAUDIBLE] brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, it's all been straightened out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, you know, I was very nervous yesterday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I says, I-- I appreciate everything you have done for me, but I am not going to go back there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I'm just going to bring the car back tonight and I hope you [LAUGHS] understand this because I'm still very chicken.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they opened up a new hotel in-- do you really want to know all this stuff-- opened up a hotel called Terrace Plaza.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On top of the-- on top of the roof, they had a small restaurant that only seated 50 people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were looking for waiters who can operate this kind of service, which all of a sudden, I became an expert on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the opening was-- and the dress where they gave us a tuxedo but we had to provide the shirts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the shirts had to be ring collars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in those years, you couldn't find-- today you can-- everybody has these shirts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So finally, I find a place where they sell you these paper [LAUGHS] collars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you had to have a shirt separate, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's that's what they demanded, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, the opening night the air condition cracks out, right, [LAUGHS] and all of a sudden, my collar pops.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
